data.title: Robert L. Martin Will Marry Ann Redman, Pembroke '64
data.text:
SUMMIT, N. J., May 9 —A September wedding is planned by Miss Ann Marie Redman and Robert Lanham Martin. Their engagement has been made known by Miss Red­man's parents, Mr. and Mrs. Byron B. Redman. Mr. Martin is the son of Mr. and Mrs. W. Claggett Martin of Franklin Lakes.

The prospective bride is a senior and is president of the Student Government Associa­tion at Pembroke College. After graduation she will join the Massachusetts Institute of Technology Instrumentation Laboratory in Cambridge, Mass. Her father is vice president and controller of the Continental Insurance Companies.

Mr. Martin, a senior at Brown University, plans to enter M.I.T. in September to study for a master's degree in electronic engineering. He is captain of the Brown swimming team.
